{"tid":835368,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult片】黑色幽默小清新《水牛66》(1998)","createTime":"2018-09-24T22:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T12:18:37.000Z","uid":212112,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63ce5194724de4b039e6f686d145a93d6a71b516","tid":835368,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T22:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/064114_eb557a7dd4067bcb86ee00d981eb2a3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F064114_eb557a7dd4067bcb86ee00d981eb2a3e.png&h=037d0721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情講述倒霉的男主角替人頂罪坐了5年監，他出獄後，但是他的霉運似乎還沒有結束，剛出獄的男主角想上廁所小便時，不是廁所維修就是被拒絕；即使鬼鬼祟祟的躲到汽車後面想就地解決時汽車也馬上開走了。<br />\n男主角和雙親的關系並不好，但他一直想修復與父母的關系。即使坐監，他也想方設法瞞著家裡，他告訴他們這5年自己在外打拼，已功成名就，並承諾將帶著女友回家。為了實現承諾，他綁架了一名女子作為自己的女友。可是，當男主角帶著她回到家裡時，事情並沒有預想中順利⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/064116_bac3217ef6ac463efc7ee30a72cefba1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F064116_bac3217ef6ac463efc7ee30a72cefba1.png&h=5cb65177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個很簡單的故事，看似像80年代以前的電影，如果不是看上映日期還真看不出來是90年代底的。<br />\nBaby face，小鼻子，可愛的女主角Christina Ricci，因為有她而精彩。觀看影片的我也能被女主角的溫柔的可愛氣質打動。<br />\nVincent Gallo在這片洋溢的才氣已經不僅僅是自編自導自演那麼簡單。他一手包辦了所有的詞曲創作，還有在片尾懶洋洋的聲音，與他那張落魄的臉一樣，充盈著未滿的憂傷和荒涼。離絕望，差那麼一點點，離圓滿，同樣隔著幾步。另外值得一提的是剪輯分鏡手法也有新意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/064117_ec7300a8f4594f57dab8c25a6a4f8836.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F064117_ec7300a8f4594f57dab8c25a6a4f8836.png&h=c956d1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/064119_cbc67a4dfb35f1ffc33467cdb12813d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F064119_cbc67a4dfb35f1ffc33467cdb12813d9.png&h=52473aae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/064120_9fa9ccc575303807426d0266d6a735ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F064120_9fa9ccc575303807426d0266d6a735ba.png&h=b0ee4e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/Bm7nZdSF9vN/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBm7nZdSF9vN%2F&d=oyvo2Xof1Dfj9cNK2k1axleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=8124def0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBm7nZdSF9vN%2F&h=4922a6e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/Bm7nZdSF9vN/</a>"},{"pid":"a44fc24398aa3a07a4282e544fe06bde347bd1ca","tid":835368,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4146fd50060d5dc4e1e61c190dab2bd6d278282","tid":835368,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:56:20.000Z","msg":"女主角係《愛登士家庭》個星期三 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/075535_3dbab543dbfa58581e732179a353d75e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F075535_3dbab543dbfa58581e732179a353d75e.jpg&h=80f2a671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/075538_b117b53679dc202eabb1cb7ae73ae261.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F075538_b117b53679dc202eabb1cb7ae73ae261.jpeg&h=4d9ca13e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97319602373444109d02815555ee4d0c36793ef3","tid":835368,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4146fd50060d5dc4e1e61c190dab2bd6d278282","tid":835368,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"